---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';

const coverages = [
  { name: 'Critical Illness Insurance', href: '/financial-services/critical-illness-insurance/' },
  { name: 'Disability Insurance', href: '/financial-services/disability-insurance/' },
  { name: 'Life Insurance', href: '/financial-services/life-insurance/' },
  { name: 'Combination Insurance', href: '/financial-services/combination-insurance/' },
  { name: 'Health & Dental Insurance', href: '/financial-services/individual-health-dental-plans/' },
  { name: 'Travel Insurance', href: '/financial-services/travel-insurance/' },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insurance Planning | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Life, critical illness, disability, and health insurance solutions for Ontario families. Independent advice on the coverage that fits your situation."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Insurance</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Currently less than 43% of Canadians have individual life insurance in place. This is a serious problem! The risk of a premature death may seem like an unlikely possibility, but it happens far too often. This is why Heidi has made it her mission to put proper protection in place for families of all ages. She has seen numerous cases where an unexpected death has changed the lives of a family forever. Having sufficient life insurance in place can make all the difference to those left behind.</p>
        <p>This problem can be solved with a relatively inexpensive life insurance policy to protect the ones' you love. Don't leave them financially devastated. Request your no-obligation quote today!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-2">
        {coverages.map(item => (
          <a href={item.href} class="group flex items-center gap-3 border border-brand-plum/10 px-5 py-3 hover:border-brand-plum/25 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
            <span class="flex-1 font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum group-hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">{item.name}</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
        <p>Heidi Blondin offers personalized, professional service in a comfortable and honest environment. No matter what your age, health, or risk factors, Heidi can deliver quality insurance solutions at rates you can afford.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-4" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Dedicated To Client Satisfaction</h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">Whether you're looking for life insurance for yourself or a loved one, Heidi can make the process informative and as smooth as possible. She has strong relationships with numerous insurance carriers across Canada. She uses her expertise and precision to detail, to narrow down the best and most cost effective options for you to choose from. She will explain the terms and conditions and help you make an informed decision.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-4" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">At Your Service</h2>
          <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>As an established Kingston, ON, life insurance advisor, Heidi Blondin proudly serves customers throughout Eastern Ontario. For your convenience, she offers flexible appointment times, online applications and quick response to all inquiries.</p>
            <p>To schedule a consultation, call today.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-brand-tintPlum border-l-4 border-brand-plum/40 p-8">
        <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/55 italic mb-4 leading-relaxed">"Dear Heidi,<br />Thank you for helping me put the right insurance in place to protect my family and I in the event of illness or death. I really appreciated the time you took to walk me through the many options. I learned a great deal throughout the process which allowed me to make an informed decision. In the end we put in place a nice combination of products to suit my requirements and budget. With proper coverage in place I have peace of mind knowing my family will be safe.<br />Thanks again for all your help!"</p>
        <p class="font-sans text-xs font-semibold text-brand-plum/70">LW – Kingston, Ontario</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Find the right coverage" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll help you understand exactly what you need to protect your family." />

</BaseLayout>
